text: Collect sample from user area then perform OCP then send sample to the third slot.
Take sample 1 from first slot, perform CA then send sample to the user area.
Take sample from user area then put the sample in the fourth slot.
Take sample from user area, perform first OCP then CA then bring the sample back to user area.
Take sample from slot 1 then put it in slot 2 then take it back and put it in slot 3.
